body.description: Our Diaper PANTS are designed with special love for your baby. High absorption capacity, soft, with a textile layer, dermotologically tested. The materials we use for our diapers ARTICLE protect the baby's delicate skin from rashes and irritation and are environmentally friendly. Especially ideal for night time use! The soft and porous surface allows air to circulate so that the baby's skin breathes freely. The inner super absorbent layer distributes the liquid evenly and turns it into a gel so that the liquid does not come into contact with the skin and the child's skin always remains dry and healthy The anatomical shape of the diapers is great for children, no matter how active they are
